==English==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|forecasten}}, {{m|enm|forcasten}}, equivalent to {{prefix|en|fore|cast}}.
The noun is from {{inh|en|enm|forecast}}, {{m|enm|forcast}}.

